toEncryptedMap

public java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> toEncryptedMap(java.lang.String clientSideEncryptionKey)
Returns an encrypted map of the card details, suitable for vaulting.

Note: This method uses a 2-digit string year (unlike getExpirationYear()) and a 2-digit string month (unlike getExpirationMonth()).

Parameters:
clientSideEncryptionKey - Braintree client-side encryption key
Returns:
a map containing KEY_ACCOUNT_NUMBER, KEY_CVV, KEY_EXPIRATION_YEAR, KEY_EXPIRATION_MONTH, and KEY_ZIPCODE, in encrypted form
